      <div class="time">00:03 - 00:07</div>
      <div class="text">发生言语争吵、挑衅</div>
    </div>
    <div class="evi">
      <div class="time">00:07 - 00:12</div>
      <div class="text">出现推搡、肢体冲突</div>
    </div>
    <div class="evi">
      <div class="time">00:15 - 00:20</div>
      <div class="text">一方倒地，声称受伤</div>
    </div>
    <div class="evi">
      <div
